<h1 id="installing-termgraph">Installing Termgraph</h1>
<p>You must use pip to install it, example:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">python <span class="nt">-m</span> pip <span class="nb">install </span>termgraph</code></pre></figure>

<p>Alternatively you can use pipx:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash">pipx <span class="nb">install </span>termgraph</code></pre></figure>

<h1 id="supported-chart-types">Supported chart types</h1>

<ul>
  <li>Bar Graphs</li>
  <li>Color charts</li>
  <li>Multi-variable</li>
  <li>Stacked charts</li>
  <li>Histograms</li>
  <li>Horizontal or Vertical</li>
  <li>Emoji!</li>
</ul>

